name: Jaime L. Garcia
text: 3 slots boardgames, 1 slot Dresden Files, 1 slot game guides, 2 slots (probably obsolete) text books on Computer Science and Business, 1 slot Harry Potter saga, 1 slot assorted scifi, 1 slot assorted fact books that aren't encyclopedias, 1 slot video-game-rela ted stories (Halo, Starcraft, Warcraft), random nerf guns, and misc. trinkets dispersed across the shelving.
